            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Welcome! ...You're that girly from the medicine shop."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x20f,
            "name_id": 0x25,
            "extra_id": 0x207,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "You're like the only young person who rides on my balloons."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x20f,
            "name_id": 0x25,
            "extra_id": 0x20c,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "You're totally my best customer.<CR>You never get tired of this, huh?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x34,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Hahaha, it's very handy. I'm sure I'll be using this service a lot from now on..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x20f,
            "name_id": 0x25,
            "extra_id": 0x207,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Is that so? Then I need to think of something to give you in exchange for your favors."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x35,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "In e-exchange...? That totally isn't necessary."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x36,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Buuut, I would like to go to other places. Is that possible?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x20f,
            "name_id": 0x25,
            "extra_id": 0x207,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Other places, huh? That's a bit tricky. I have other customers and it'll be hard to ensure your safety..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x20f,
            "name_id": 0x25,
            "extra_id": 0x207,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Oh, I know! With how often you use these, buying one is one way to go."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x20f,
            "name_id": 0x25,
            "extra_id": 0x20c,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "If you don't mind a used one, I'll sell you one. It won't be cheap, but how 'bout it?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Whoa, I guess you weren't kidding about it not being cheap..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x20f,
            "name_id": 0x25,
            "extra_id": 0x207,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Hahaha, you don't need to give me an answer right away. When you've made up your mind, come talk to me again."
